screen_desc: The screenshot displays a food delivery app interface showing the user's cart from "Bradman Pizza house." It lists a single item, a 9-inch Supreme pizza priced at $14.95. There are options for delivery or pickup, and a section titled "Complement your cart" with images of additional food items. Below, there is a prompt to "Select Payment Method," offering options including Credit/Debit Card, Google Pay, PayPal, and Afterpay.
